    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >PALE HUNT 是一款带有恐怖元素的开放世界怪物狩猎模拟游戏。一次普通的旅行因意外终结，你被困在深夜的泰加林中——手无寸铁，毫无准备。为了看到黎明，你必须追踪并消灭那些正在猎杀你的可怕生物。 探索环境，搜寻装备，寻找对抗敌人的方法。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索开放世界 呈现在你面前的是一大片原始森林。你可以自由前往任何地方：探索茂密的灌木丛，穿越杂草前往废弃的猎人小屋，在旧旅游路线上寻找踪迹。但请记住：你深入森林越远，回来的机会就越渺茫。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4316480/extras/f03cfb68a3fd58a32d5f6505c77d1d6d.poster.avif?t=1770371222\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4316480/extras/f03cfb68a3fd58a32d5f6505c77d1d6d.webm?t=1770371222\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4316480/extras/f03cfb68a3fd58a32d5f6505c77d1d6d.mp4?t=1770371222\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >狩猎 敌人比你更快、更强，因此正面冲突对你不利。为了生存，你必须像猎人一样思考。用听觉侦测灌木丛中的动静。凝视树下的黑暗，研究怪物的习性。利用你的武器和装备，调查该区域并举行仪式来找到你的目标。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4316480/extras/1d90d073d2b3bb5121fee6536ab46d69.poster.avif?t=1770371222\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4316480/extras/1d90d073d2b3bb5121fee6536ab46d69.webm?t=1770371222\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4316480/extras/1d90d073d2b3bb5121fee6536ab46d69.mp4?t=1770371222\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >生存 你的武器陈旧且不顺手，因此每一发子弹都必须深思熟虑。你必须搜寻装备，以增加在这片危险森林中的生存几率。利用你的技能和环境，尝试用不同的方法解决问题，寻找捷径以获得对敌人的优势。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4316480/extras/8913fd272a62cab32342d24f0225549b.poster.avif?t=1770371222\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4316480/extras/8913fd272a62cab32342d24f0225549b.webm?t=1770371222\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4316480/extras/8913fd272a62cab32342d24f0225549b.mp4?t=1770371222\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主要特色：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >开放世界。 可供自由探索的大片森林区域：从茂密的灌木丛和开阔的田野到废弃的猎人小屋和旅游小径。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >非线性游戏。 游戏不会手把手教你。解决同一个问题有多种方法——只能依靠你自己。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >成长。 搜寻武器和补给，利用技能系统和环境来提高生存几率。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >狩猎。 敌人比你更快、更强。利用听觉、观察和仪式，在敌人发现你之前发现他们。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >难度。 你的武器古老且笨重。正面冲突往往会导致死亡。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >氛围。 沉浸在深夜森林的神秘、恐怖和令人窒息的孤独中。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4316480/extras/af0c7f041abb83f8944c0d1c1ab642ef.poster.avif?t=1770371222\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4316480/extras/af0c7f041abb83f8944c0d1c1ab642ef.webm?t=1770371222\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4316480/extras/af0c7f041abb83f8944c0d1c1ab642ef.mp4?t=1770371222\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
